overview: Kayton Shades and Blinds Melbourne formerly AABack Venetian Blinds Melbourne has traded for over 25 years almost exclusively to real estate agents and property developers throughout Melbourne. We have recently switched up gears and are now supplying blinds and shutters to the general public. We don’t have the overheads of a traditional blinds & shutters retail store and we don’t employ sales people or run expensive marketing campaigns. Our cost base is low and we pass the savings onto our customers. We supply and install the best blinds, shutters and shades available in the market at the lowest prices.
